### Test 1: Unknown host returns 404
GET http://localhost:8080/
Host: unknown.host.com
X-Api-Key: testuser1234

?? status == 404

### Test 2: Known host proxies to upstream (echo server on 9090)
GET http://localhost:8080/hello
Host: echo.local
X-Api-Key: testuser1234

?? status == 200
?? body includes hello from upstream

### Test 3: Missing API key returns 401
GET http://localhost:8080/
Host: echo.local

?? status == 401

### Test 4: Missing env var for secret returns 500
# Without fnox exec, OPENAI_API_KEY is unset so env:// resolution fails
GET http://localhost:8080/v1/models
Host: openai.internal.domain.com
X-Api-Key: testuser1234

?? status == 500

### Test 5: POST body is forwarded
POST http://localhost:8080/echo
Host: echo.local
X-Api-Key: testuser1234
Content-Type: application/json

{"message": "proxied"}

?? status == 200
